          <div class="date-posts">
        
<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>

<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://maoistroad.blogspot.com/2022/12/galiza-honra-e-gloria-ao-camarada-jose.html'>&#160; GALIZA: HONRA E GLORIA AO CAMARADA JOSE MARIA SISÓN (Galiza Vermelha) </a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-3401145946208259731' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<br /><div class="post-header">
<div class="post-header-line-1"></div>
</div>

<p>&nbsp;</p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjLf5TJ5NVMGsiN4H7MNxBVZoKQrfynEnwB-_sZdYGlmDxdbLQjwK2hZcj3p-DQIQ3-k9EBL0owaLeUug0kjbwYIu89-2KX9xfeKjllFClGs4tzipJt4MgSuAoX1xWDYddO1-A4ObpBhiisuUYH_n1rZPc5A4SUH182pxFgYI_aaB0AuZsR4FDvIZ4Xlg/s678/FkVP4kaWQAA49rX.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="381" data-original-width="678" height="248" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjLf5TJ5NVMGsiN4H7MNxBVZoKQrfynEnwB-_sZdYGlmDxdbLQjwK2hZcj3p-DQIQ3-k9EBL0owaLeUug0kjbwYIu89-2KX9xfeKjllFClGs4tzipJt4MgSuAoX1xWDYddO1-A4ObpBhiisuUYH_n1rZPc5A4SUH182pxFgYI_aaB0AuZsR4FDvIZ4Xlg/w441-h248/FkVP4kaWQAA49rX.jpg" width="441" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><p></p><p><span style="background-color: white; color: #0f1419; font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 23px; white-space: pre-wrap;">José Maria Sison tamém conhecido como Ka Joma (1939-2022) era um revolucionário das Filipinas. Ele foi fundador do Partido Comunista das Filipinas, do Novo Exército do Povo e do Frente Democrático Nacional.</span></p><p><span style="background-color: white; color: #0f1419; font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 23px; white-space: pre-wrap;">As pessoas que vivem e morrem pola revoluçom sempre vivem no coraçom do proletariado revolucionário dos povos do mundo.

Honra e glória!</span></p>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>

<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Sison-copia.jpg' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='7106337660494808516' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='1976139580927091203' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='1976139580927091203'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://maoistroad.blogspot.com/2022/12/colombia-honor-y-gloria-al-camarada.html'>&#160; COLOMBIA: &#161;Honor y gloria al camarada Jose Maria Sison! </a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-1976139580927091203' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<br /><div class="post-header">
<div class="post-header-line-1"></div>
</div>

<p><br /></p><div class="clear" style="background-color: white; border: 0px; clear: both; color: #666666; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14.08px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; height: 0px; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: hidden; width: 0px;"></div><div class="entry themeform fittexted_for_entry" style="background-color: white; border: 0px; color: #666666; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><div class="entry-inner" style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><div class="wp-block-image" style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><figure class="aligncenter size-full" style="border: 0px; clear: both; display: table; font: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><a href="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Sison-copia.jpg" style="border: 0px; color: #fe0000; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; vertical-align: baseline;"><img alt="&#161;Honor y gloria al camarada Jose Maria Sison! 1" class="wp-image-15975" height="340" src="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Sison-copia.jpg" style="border-radius: inherit; border: 0px; font: inherit; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease 0s; vertical-align: bottom;" width="340" /></a></figure></div><p style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"></p><p style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Los
 camaradas del Partido Comunista de Filipinas han informado sobre el 
fallecimiento del camarada Jose Maria Sison este 16 de diciembre, luego 
de estar dos semanas en confinamiento en un hospital. Tenía 83 años. El 
camarada Ka Joma fue un comunista, revolucionario, internacionalista y 
ferviente luchador por la liberación nacional del pueblo filipino. 
Fundador y dirigente del Partido Comunista de Filipinas, así como del 
Nuevo Ejército del Pueblo (NPA). Su muerte tiene el &#8220;peso de una 
montaña&#8221; para el proletariado y las masas oprimidas en Filipinas.</p><p style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Desde
 muy joven, el camarada Sison se vinculó al movimiento revolucionario. 
Desde su etapa como estudiante, junto a otros jóvenes rebeldes formaron 
la Asociación Cultural Estudiantil de la Universidad de Filipinas con el
 fin de librar la lucha ideológica en torno a los problemas de la 
sociedad filipina y el estudio del marxismo-leninismo. Después fue 
militante del Partido del Trabajo y uno de los organizadores de la&nbsp;<em style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Kabataang Makabayan</em>&nbsp;(Juventud
 Patriótica) en la década del sesenta. Posteriormente, siendo parte del 
Partido Comunista de Filipinas, mediante el Primer Gran Movimiento de 
Rectificación impulsaría la lucha de dos líneas contra el oportunismo de
 derecha y de &#8220;izquierda&#8221; que existía dentro del partido dando como 
resultado su reconstitución un 26 de diciembre de 1968 (en el 
septuagésimo quinto aniversario del natalicio del Presidente Mao 
Tse-tung). Al año siguiente se fundaría el Nuevo Ejército del Pueblo 
como brazo armado del partido e instrumento para emprender la guerra 
popular que a día de hoy se sigue desarrollando en las montañas 
filipinas. En ese mismo año de 1969, el camarada Sison publica su 
principal obra titulada&nbsp;<em style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Sociedad y Revolución Filipina,&nbsp;</em>en
 donde expone desde el marxismo-leninismo-maoísmo el desarrollo de la 
sociedad filipina, su carácter como país semifeudal y semicolonial y, 
por consiguiente, establece que la revolución debería ser democrático 
popular dirigida por el proletariado. El camarada Sison, bajo el nombre 
político de &#8220;Amado Guerrero&#8221;, sería presidente del partido entre 1968 
hasta 1977, año en que fue capturado junto a su compañera Ka Julie por 
el régimen dictatorial de Ferdinand Marcos, siendo liberado en 1986 tras
 el derrocamiento de la dictadura. Viviendo en el exilio en Países Bajos
 desde 1987, estuvo siempre pendiente del proceso revolucionario en su 
país natal e impulsando el apoyo a las luchas populares en el mundo.</p><p style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">La
 muerte de Joma ocurre luego de la del camarada Zia en 2020 en 
Afganistán y del presidente Gonzalo en 2021 en Perú, los cuales 
comparten una misma generación que se forjó teniendo como inspiración a 
la GRCP en China, comparten importantes aportes teóricos y prácticos a 
los movimientos revolucionarios en sus respectivos países, y hoy ponen 
de presente la necesidad de nuevos dirigentes que se inspiren en estos 
grandes camaradas.</p><p style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">La
 Unión Obrera Comunista (mlm) lamenta el fallecimiento del camarada Jose
 Maria Sison y envía un saludo internacionalista y revolucionario a los 
abnegados militantes y dirigentes del Partido Comunista de Filipinas, a 
los valerosos combatientes del Nuevo Ejército del Pueblo, a los 
luchadores del Frente Democrático Nacional, y a toda la clase obrera y 
masas populares filipinas. Estaremos seguros que la memoria del camarada
 Jose Maria Sison estará presente en todos los que luchan por la 
revolución y la liberación nacional del pueblo filipino.</p><p style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Comité de Dirección &#8211; Unión Obrera Comunista (mlm)</p><p style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Colombia, 18 de diciembre de 2022.</p></div></div>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>

<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='https://moolbato.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jose_Maria_Sison_portrait.jpg.webp' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='7106337660494808516' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='7715375136456984379' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='7715375136456984379'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://maoistroad.blogspot.com/2022/12/nepal-message-of-condolence-of-cpn.html'>&#160; NEPAL: Message of condolence of CPN (Revolutionary Maoist) : &#8216;Our party pays heartfelt homage to Comrade Sison&#8217; </a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-7715375136456984379' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<br /><div class="post-header">
<div class="post-header-line-1"></div>
</div>

<blockquote style="border: none; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;"><section class="main-content pt-0 mt-20" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 50px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px !important; position: relative;"><div class="container" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1260px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; width: 1260px;"><div class="row ts-gutter-30" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: -15px !important; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-top: -15px !important;"><div class="col-lg-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; flex: 0 0 75%; max-width: 75%; padding-bottom: 15px !important; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 15px !important; position: relative; width: 945px;"><div class="single-post" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div class="post-header-area" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div class="single__post__image" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Ek Mukta&quot;; font-size: 14px; position: relative; text-align: left;"><img class="img-fluid mb-20" src="https://moolbato.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Jose_Maria_Sison_portrait.jpg.webp" style="border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; margin-bottom: 20px !important; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;" /><span style="font-family: &quot;Ek Mukta&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></blockquote><p>&nbsp;<span style="font-family: &quot;Ek Mukta&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Ek Mukta&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">&#8216;Comrade
 Jose Maria Sison, the founding Chairman of the Communist Party of the 
Philippines, died at 83. He passed away last Friday at 8:40 P.M. 
Philippine time after a two-week confinement in a hospital in Utrecht, 
Netherlands.</span></p><section class="main-content pt-0 mt-20" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 50px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px !important; position: relative;"><div class="container" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1260px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; width: 1260px;"><div class="row ts-gutter-30" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: -15px !important; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-top: -15px !important;"><div class="col-lg-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; flex: 0 0 75%; max-width: 75%; padding-bottom: 15px !important; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 15px !important; position: relative; width: 945px;"><div class="single-post" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div class="post-header-area" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br />Comrade
 Sison, who had been leading the new democratic revolution in the 
Philippines since the party was founded in 1968, has made a significant 
contribution to the development of the world communist movement and the 
anti-imperialist movement as well. With his death, not only the 
communist movement of the Philippines but also the world communist 
movement lost a revolutionary communist leader. It is an immense loss 
for the world communist movement. Our party expresses strong solidarity 
with the Communist Party of the Philippines, the proletariat and the 
oppressed Philippine people in their struggle to confront this loss.<br /><br />At
 this time of grief, our party pays heartfelt homage to Comrade Sison 
and expresses deep condolence to the Central Committee of the Communist 
Party of the Philippines, the proletariat, the warriors of the New 
People&#8217;s Army, the oppressed Filipino people, his family and relatives.&#8217;<br /><br />December 18, 2022                                                         <br /><br />          Kiran<br /><br />                        General Secretary<br /><br />                     CPN (Revolutionary Maoist)</div></div></div></div></div></section>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>

<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://maoistroad.blogspot.com/2022/12/important-galiza-vermelha-china-umha.html'>important - Galiza vermelha -  China, umha nova potência Social-Imperialista</a>

<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-8779180437241993816' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p>&nbsp;</p><h1 class="entry-title">China, umha nova potência Social-Imperialista</h1>				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="byline"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="svg-icon" height="16" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"></svg></span></div><br /><div class="entry-content">
		
<p>Desde Galiza Vermelha editamos a traduçom para a nossa língua do 
texto &#8220;China, umha nova potência Social-Imperialista&#8221;, umha análise 
imprescindível do Partido Comunista da Índia (maoista). Tanto a ediçom 
digital como a ediçom impressa som ferramentas úteis para a formaçom do 
proletariado galego</p><p>.<span class="markedContent"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid0"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid1"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 20.9534px; left: 95.0169px; top: 36.907px; transform: scaleX(0.851444);">INTRODUÇOM DE GALIZA VERMELHA PARA ESTA EDIÇOM</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid2"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid3"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid4"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid5"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid6"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 92.0932px; transform: scaleX(0.90234);">O PCI(maoista) é agora mesmo o maior Partido Comunista do mundo. Ademais</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid7"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 114.863px; transform: scaleX(0.93086);">este Partido Comunista está dirigindo o maior Exército Vermelho existente na</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid8"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 137.632px; transform: scaleX(0.93647);">atua</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid9"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 83.5623px; top: 137.632px; transform: scaleX(0.935235);">lidade, na sua Guerra Popular contra o poder dum estado burguês semi</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid10"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 637.799px; top: 137.632px;">-</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid11"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 160.262px; transform: scaleX(0.915839);">feudal, mas que é umha potência nuclear. O novo poder revolucionário está</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid12"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 621.456px; top: 160.262px;">-</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid13"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 627.183px; top: 160.262px; transform: scaleX(0.841961);">se</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid14"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 183.031px; transform: scaleX(1.02186);">consolidando nas bases de apoio da Índia e é precisamente isto o que</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid15"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 205.8px; transform: scaleX(0.937381);">transforma ao PCI(maoista) num referente</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid16"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 376.798px; top: 205.8px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 382.691px; top: 205.8px; transform: scaleX(0.94544);">para o proletariado consciente de</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid17"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 228.57px; transform: scaleX(0.958715);">todos os povos. Esta realidade é conhecida polo maoismo galego do que a</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid18"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 251.2px; transform: scaleX(0.914119);">nossa organizaçom forma parte.</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid19"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid20"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid21"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 283.328px; transform: scaleX(0.955653);">O avanço na integraçom entre a teoria</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid22"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid23"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 352.627px; top: 283.328px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 357.244px; top: 283.328px; transform: scaleX(0.936271);">revolucionária</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid24"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid25"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 465.54px; top: 283.328px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 469.858px; top: 283.328px; transform: scaleX(0.939439);">como a imprescindível</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid26"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 306.133px; transform: scaleX(0.904258);">guia</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 81.3594px; top: 306.133px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 92.6924px; top: 306.133px; transform: scaleX(0.915362);">para</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 126.729px; top: 306.133px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 138.062px; top: 306.133px; transform: scaleX(0.911079);">açom</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 179.455px; top: 306.133px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 190.714px; top: 306.133px; transform: scaleX(0.886443);">coa</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 217.263px; top: 306.133px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 228.559px; top: 306.133px; transform: scaleX(0.941151);">prática</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 281.043px; top: 306.133px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 292.339px; top: 306.133px; transform: scaleX(0.891778);">social</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 334.699px; top: 306.133px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 346.088px; top: 306.133px; transform: scaleX(0.914956);">consciente</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid27"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid28"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 427.351px; top: 306.133px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 438.986px; top: 306.133px; transform: scaleX(0.945717);">do</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 458.531px; top: 306.133px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 469.845px; top: 306.133px; transform: scaleX(0.954655);">proletariado,</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 568.461px; top: 306.133px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 579.701px; top: 306.133px; transform: scaleX(0.954951);">unido</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 623.12px; top: 306.133px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 634.434px; top: 306.133px;">à</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid29"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 328.762px; transform: scaleX(0.907707);">necessidade de que esta prática social poda pola sua parte alimentar à teoria é</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid30"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 351.532px; transform: scaleX(0.929702);">umha necessidade, um problema real do Movimento Comunista Internacional</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid31"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 374.301px; transform: scaleX(0.929684);">(MCI) neste momento. A soluçom deste problema implica dar</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid32"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 519.482px; top: 374.301px;">-</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid33"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 525.21px; top: 374.301px; transform: scaleX(0.915866);">lhe um especial</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid34"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 397.07px; transform: scaleX(1.00737);">prot</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid35"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 81.886px; top: 397.07px; transform: scaleX(0.931743);">agonismo ao fator consciente, a necessidade de entender e transfomar o</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid36"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 419.7px; transform: scaleX(0.926755);">mundo conscientemente. É imprescindível conhecer a história do proletariado</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid37"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 442.47px; transform: scaleX(0.943981);">revolucionário</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 158.777px; top: 442.47px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 172.432px; top: 442.47px; transform: scaleX(0.915362);">para</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 206.468px; top: 442.47px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 220.18px; top: 442.47px; transform: scaleX(0.939824);">criar</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 254.123px; top: 442.47px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 267.778px; top: 442.47px;">a</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 276.677px; top: 442.47px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 290.389px; top: 442.47px; transform: scaleX(0.866965);">nossa</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 333.361px; top: 442.47px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 347.202px; top: 442.47px; transform: scaleX(0.912311);">cosmovisom,</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 446.097px; top: 442.47px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 459.734px; top: 442.47px;">a</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 468.633px; top: 442.47px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 482.344px; top: 442.47px; transform: scaleX(0.866965);">nossa</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 525.316px; top: 442.47px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 539.046px; top: 442.47px; transform: scaleX(0.914562);">nova</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 575.888px; top: 442.47px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 589.599px; top: 442.47px; transform: scaleX(0.958142);">cultura</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid38"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 465.239px; transform: scaleX(0.93974);">revolucionária. É imprescindível conhecer</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid39"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 372.767px; top: 465.239px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 380.037px; top: 465.239px; transform: scaleX(0.917276);">as mudanças sociais, económicas,</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid40"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 488.008px; transform: scaleX(0.904786);">políticas, culturais e militares que se dérom até hoje. É imprescindível conhecer</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid41"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 510.661px; transform: scaleX(0.988673);">as evoluçons e transformaçons dos estados burgueses e muito mais dos</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid42"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 533.431px; transform: scaleX(0.910884);">estados que algum dia fôrom socialistas.</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid43"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid44"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid45"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 565.559px; transform: scaleX(0.915533);">É por isto desde Galiza Vermelh</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid46"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 292.987px; top: 565.559px; transform: scaleX(0.932032);">a consideramos que o presente texto, &#8220;China:</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid47"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 588.189px; transform: scaleX(0.90207);">umha nova potência Social</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid48"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 251.08px; top: 588.189px;">-</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid49"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 256.808px; top: 588.189px; transform: scaleX(0.928289);">Imperialista!&#8221; é umha obra útil para a formaçom do</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid50"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 610.958px; transform: scaleX(0.922469);">proletariado galego. Trata</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid51"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 245.493px; top: 610.958px;">-</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid52"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 251.22px; top: 610.958px; transform: scaleX(0.901392);">se dumha análise sobre a restauraçom capitalista na</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid53"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 633.728px; transform: scaleX(0.939347);">China, sobre qual foi o rumo ditado polo revisionismo,</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid54"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 465.846px; top: 633.728px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 471.394px; top: 633.728px; transform: scaleX(0.936614);">sobre o papel atual do</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid55"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 656.497px; transform: scaleX(0.912095);">Estado Chinês na distribuiçom mundial capitalista, sobre como se tornou umha</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid56"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 679.127px; transform: scaleX(0.914562);">nova</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 86.4314px; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 166.952px; top: 679.127px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 181.499px; top: 679.127px; transform: scaleX(0.894125);">social</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid57"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 224.26px; top: 679.127px;">-</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid58"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 229.987px; top: 679.127px; transform: scaleX(0.942708);">imperialista,</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 323.457px; top: 679.127px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 337.837px; top: 679.127px; transform: scaleX(0.905139);">sendo</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 383.652px; top: 679.127px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 398.292px; top: 679.127px; transform: scaleX(0.959864);">parte</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 438.942px; top: 679.127px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 453.545px; top: 679.127px; transform: scaleX(0.952908);">do</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 473.238px; top: 679.127px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 487.73px; top: 679.127px; transform: scaleX(0.906347);">sistema</span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 545.751px; top: 679.127px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 560.428px; top: 679.127px; transform: scaleX(0.933058);">capitalista</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid59"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 638.079px; top: 679.127px;">-</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid60"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 701.896px; transform: scaleX(0.941512);">imperialista mundial e sobre como se tornou um inimigo das naçons e povos</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid61"><br role="presentation" /><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 49.5898px; top: 724.701px; transform: scaleX(0.941481);">oprimidos do</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid62"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid63"><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 149.748px; top: 724.701px;"> </span><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 18.5787px; left: 153.961px; top: 724.701px; transform: scaleX(0.94717);">mundo.</span></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid64"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid65"></span><span class="markedContent" id="page12R_mcid66"><br role="presentation" /><br /></span></p></div>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>

<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='https://www.demvolkedienen.org/images/Indien/Malta-Aktion-Volkskrieg_in_Indien.png' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='7106337660494808516' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='1648813803564424492' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='1648813803564424492'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://maoistroad.blogspot.com/2022/12/solidarity-with-india-revolution-from.html'>Solidarity with India revolution from Malta - Association Red Pages very good</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-1648813803564424492' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<div class="nav-collapse">
						<ul class="nav menu nav-pills"><li class="item-101"><h2>Malta: Solidaridad con la Revolución en la India</h2>



<p>El 11 de diciembre, la Asociación Páginas Rojas y la Organización de 
Estudiantes Independientes de Malta llevaron a cabo por primera vez una 
acción de solidaridad con la Revolución en la India.</p>



<p>Se informó de que los activistas han dado a conocer el movimiento 
popular y la guerra popular en la India y han difundido la lucha del 
pueblo de la India también en la isla de Malta. Estas acciones fueron 
puestas en relación con la situación del pueblo de Malta.</p>



<p>El régimen fascista de Modi fue denunciado en las actividades, y al 
mismo tiempo la cuestión del reino imperialista y la influencia 
extranjera en la India no quedó sin atención. En el centro estaba la 
lucha por la revolución, contra el imperialismo y las relaciones 
feudales. El ejemplo indio muestra, se informó, que una revolución es 
completamente posible en estos tiempos. Además, &#161;se anunciaron más 
acciones para los días cercanos a Navidad!</p></li></ul>

					</div>
				
						
			
								
					
					
					<div id="system-message-container">
	</div>

					
	
	
		
			<div class="page-header">
		<h2 itemprop="name">
							Malta: Solidarität mit der Revolution in Indien					</h2>
							</div>
					
	
	
		
						    	<div class="pull-left item-image"> <img alt="" height="421" itemprop="image" src="https://www.demvolkedienen.org/images/Indien/Malta-Aktion-Volkskrieg_in_Indien.png" width="640" /> </div>
	    			<div itemprop="articleBody">
		<p style="text-align: justify;"><i>Wir veröffentlichen eine inoffizielle Übersetzung eines Artikels, der auf der <a href="https://ci-ic.org/blog/2022/12/23/malta-solidarity-with-the-revolution-in-india/">Website Communist International</a> veröffentlicht wurde.</i></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Am 11. Dezember wurde zum ersten Mal 
eine Solidaritätsaktion mit der Revolution in Indien von der Association
 Red Pages und der Unabhängigen Studentenorganisation von Malta 
durchgeführt.</p>
 
<p style="text-align: justify;">Es wurde berichtet, dass die Aktivisten 
die Volksbewegung und den Volkskrieg in Indien bekannt gemacht und den 
Kampf des indischen Volkes auch auf der Insel Malta verbreitet haben. 
Diese Aktionen wurden in Zusammenhang mit der Situation der Menschen auf
 Malta gebracht.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Bei den Aktivitäten wurde das 
faschistische Modi-Regime angeprangert, und gleichzeitig wurde die Frage
 der imperialistischen Herrschaft und des ausländischen Einflusses in 
Indien nicht unbeachtet gelassen. Im Mittelpunkt stand der Kampf für die
 Revolution, gegen den Imperialismus und die feudalen Verhältnisse. Das 
indische Beispiel zeige, wurde berichtet, dass eine Revolution in diesen
 Zeiten durchaus möglich sei. Zusätzlich wurden weitere Aktionen für die
 Tage um Weihnachten angekündigt!</p>	</div><p>&nbsp;</p>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>

          <div class="date-outer">
        
<h2 class='date-header'><span>Tuesday, December 20, 2022</span></h2>

          <div class="date-posts">
        
<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='data:image/jpeg;base64,' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='7106337660494808516' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='3168070493218746220' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='3168070493218746220'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://maoistroad.blogspot.com/2022/12/prof-jose-maria-sison-8-february-1939.html'>Prof. Jose Maria Sison (8 February 1939 - 16 December 2022) - NDF International Office</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-3168070493218746220' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<h1 class="western"><span style="color: black;">&nbsp;</span><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;">The
Filipino proletariat and toiling peoples grieve the death of their
teacher and guiding light. Prof. Jose Maria Sison, Founding Chairman
of the Communist Party of the Philippines and Chief Political
Consultant of the National Democratic Front of the Philippines,
passed away peacefully in the early afternoon of 16 December, after
two weeks&#8217; confinement in a hospital in Utrecht, The Netherlands.
He was 83.</span></span></h1>
<p style="line-height: 107%; margin-bottom: 0.29cm;"><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;">On
17 December, the CPP Central Committee said, &#8220;With Ka Joma&#8217;s
passing, the Party lost a great leader. Indeed, he is among the
greatest of Filipinos of the past century for masterfully and
creatively applying Marxism-Leninism-Maoism to the Philippines and
the Philippine revolution, and giving the Filipino people the
strength to carve the country&#8217;s future and attain their aspirations
for national freedom and democracy.&#8221;</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 107%; margin-bottom: 0.29cm;"><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;">The
CPP declared, &#8220;Let us forever keep red his memory and legacy and
strengthen our determination to continue and bring forward the
revolution that he ignited together with other great leaders of the
Central Committee and its Political Bureau and Executive Committee.</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 107%; margin-bottom: 0.29cm;">&#8220;<span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;">Through
his writings, Ka Joma laid out the theoretical foundation of the
Philippine revolution. He also left us with a rich and deep
Marxist-Leninist-Maoist treasure trove which will serve as guide for
the Party&#8217;s continued growth in the next stage of the Filipino
people&#8217;s revolutionary struggles.&#8221;</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 107%; margin-bottom: 0.29cm;"><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;">The
Party added, &#8220;We affirm as well the important role that Ka Joma
played as a Marxist-Leninist-Maoist torch bearer who helped inspire
the proletariat across the world, and keep the embers of the
international communist movement as it enters a new phase of
resurgence.</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 107%; margin-bottom: 0.29cm;">&#8220;<span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;">We
declare Ka Joma as the greatest hero of the Filipino people in their
past century of resistance against imperialism. His immense
contributions to shaping the patriotic and revolutionary
consciousness of the Filipino people and breaking open the path
towards national and social liberation, will never be erased,&#8221; the
CPP concluded.</span></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 107%; margin-bottom: 0.29cm;"><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;">Prof.
Sison&#8217;s remains lie in state at the Barbara Uitvaartcentrum in
Utrecht, The Netherlands. The NDFP International Office announced
that visitors are welcome on 18 &#8211; 22 December 2022, from 7:00 &#8211;
9:00pm CET. On Friday, 23 December, international groups and
political parties will hold a tribute to Ka Joma from 4:00 &#8211; 8:00pm
CET. Prof. Sison&#8217;s cremation will take place at 10:30am CET, 27
December, at the Crematorium Daelwijk in Utrecht, the NDFP confirmed.
</span></span></p><h1 class="western"><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><img alt="" height="304" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," width="400" /></span></span></span></h1><p style="line-height: 107%; margin-bottom: 0.29cm;">
</p>
<p style="line-height: 107%; margin-bottom: 0.29cm;"><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;">The
NDFP International Office further announced that messages may be sent
to </span></span><a href="mailto:kjl.msgs@protonmail.com"><span style="color: #0563c1;"><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><u>kjl.msgs@protonmail.com</u></span></span></span></a><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;">
and </span></span><a href="mailto:editors@updatesphilippines.info"><span style="color: #0563c1;"><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><u>editors@updatesphilippines.info</u></span></span></span></a><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;">.
Additional information on the wake and cremation can be accessed at
</span></span><a href="https://updatesphilippines.hosted.phplist.com/lists/lt.php?tid=KxpTAw0BAFMFCh4EVQAJFAUBBFdIDABcAE8BAFVQX1ACB1AJXA8fAwBRBwZVCwkUAQ5UVUgBClsPTwADBFAUA1pXBlEKAVJSBQVSTAYAXVsDDgdSSFcLWl1PDVFWARRUBV8LHV5WWwdTBwEBBVQKWA"><span style="color: #0563c1;"><span face="Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><u>ndfp.info</u></span></span></span></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>
